snippet.title: No Man's Sky: Omega Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing..the OMEGA update.

Whether you own the game or not, the OMEGA update invites everybody to embark upon a new shared interstellar expedition for free (from Thursday 15th to Monday 19th February 2024). Featuring a complete overhaul of expeditions, new on-planet missions, claimable pirate freighters, and much more!

Full details here: https://www.nomanssky.com/omega-update
